<h1><em>Instructions</em></h2>
<ol>
<li><em>Make yourself a good amount of french fries or use to store bought</em></li><br><li><em>ln a bowl,whisk the eggs,add salt and pepper to taste.Add french fries to the bowl and mix it all.</em></li><br><li><em>ln a pan,heat oil and add the the fried eggs mixtire to it.Cook for 3 to 4 minutes until golden from the bottom of the flip and cook the other side.</em></li><br><li><em>Serve hot with your favourite chili sauce,bread or have it as it is,and Enjoy!</em></li>
</li>
